description: The Daltons escape from prison and visit their mother.
name: Ma Dalton

description: Will is sent by his grandfather to the underground subways of New York. An army of winos transformed into Juju Zombies is being assembled, and it's up to Will to stop the growing menace! Accompanied by the sorceress Aarna and the vampire mage Delilah, Will must quickly master his new powers or be overwhelmed by the Zombie Lord!

Lucky Luke is entrusted to find a missing horse from Bronco Fortworth, who is convinced the thief is a Cheyenne indian called Tea Spoon. He offers a reward to whoever brings in the indian, and Elliot Belt, a bunty hunter,¬†is interested.
name: Chasseur de primes

description: Along with Aarna the sorceress and the vampire Delilah, William Warlock investigates a series of zombie attacks in New York's labyrinthine subways. There they meet a diabolical Zombie Lord turning slack-jawed winos and unsuspecting tourists into powerful juju zombie slaves to take over Manhattan!

After hearing of the demise of the Zombie Lord, the Queen of the Undead unleashes her minions on Warlock Manor. Meanwhile, Will Warlock, sorceress Aarna and vampiress Delilah head for the Great Saudi Arabian Desert for a little rest, relaxation, and werewolf- hunting.

William Warlock and his partners, sorceress Aarna and vampire Delilah, pose as circus performers in Midwest America to hunt werewolves. But when Will is knocked out cold and Delilah captured in her coffin in the middle of the day, can Aarna and Will's girlfriend Tayesha save them in time?

It's a Dog and Pony Show from Hell as Will, Aarna, Delilah, and Tayesha take on a circus of werewolves! Tayesha shows her stuff, tackling the Minions of Evil with motor revving and guns blazing, but it'll take all that our heroes have to muzzle the centaur-wolf form of the monstrous Werewolf King!

Will, Aarna and Delilah make a run for the border for a little Cinco de Mayhem, hunting Chupacabra in Mexico. They find something really unexpected, another team of monster hunters! Then one of these fighters discovers Delilah is a vampire... but both teams must put their differences aside or be slaughtered in the dark by night creepers!

Deep in the Mayan jungles, Will and company feel more than the heat under the assault of chupacabra cadres. Teamed up with the new monster-hunter group, led by Jericho, they may not be enough to tackle the chupacabra leader. Will they get his goat‚Äîor will the goat get them?
Lucky Luke has to protect a russian Duke as he visits the Far West to decide if he wants to sign a treaty with the americans.
name: Le grand Duc

description: Oggie Svenson moves from prison to his hotel, under Lucky Luke's surveillance. He leaves all of his fortune to Rantanplan. The testament also says that if the dog dies, the fortune would pass on to Joe Dalton. As soon as the Dalton learn this, they escape from prison.
name: L'heritage de Rantanplan

3- Maverick¬†
4- L'egal de Wyatt Earp¬†
5- Le colporteur¬†
6- Passage dangereux¬†
7- Sonate en Colt majeur
name: 7 histoires de Lucky Luke

description: Whitaker Baltimore has a ambulant theatre company. Mysteriously, there is a burglary in every town the act. Lucky Luke decides to follow its tour.
name: Le cavalier blanc

description: Professor Otto Von Himbeergeist expounds his theory at the Congress. He believes criminals are ill, and can be cured. He starts proving his ideas with the Daltons.
name: La guerison des Dalton

description: In Grass Town, Lucky Luke meets Dean Smith, a rich breeder who has lost his head an beieves he is the Emperor of the United States. With his fortune, Smith even has raised an army. The inhabitants of Grass Town see him harmless and are amused playing the game that they believe him. The bandit Buck Ritchie meets Smith and convinces him to take over the town.
name: L'empereur Smith

description:
The government offers $100.000 to the first city that builds a telegraph line to Salt Lake City. Carson, from the West, and O'Maha, in the from the East accept the challenge.

Last issue written by Goscinny.
name: Le fil qui chante

description: The Daltons learn from their cell mate that there is a pile of money buried at Red Rock Juntion. They escape and go for it, but now there is a penitentiary built at the same place.
name: Le magot des Dalton

description: Brothers Arthur and Adolphe Caille have invented a slot machine. Senator Pinball asks Lucky Luke to help them making their invention famous along the West.
name: Le bandit manchot

description: Sarah Bernhardt is touring the United States. Lucky Luke has to protect her from the League of Virtue and its president's wife.
name: Sarah Bernhardt

4- Reglement de comptes¬†
5- La bonne parole¬†
6- Li-Chi's Story
name: La corde du pendu et autres histoires

description: Lucky Luke is named the new sheriff of Daisy Town. Issue based on 1971 Lucky Luke's movie.
name: Daisy Town

description: A magician kleptomaniac called Fingers is put in jail, where he helps the Daltons escaping.
name: Fingers

description: Horace Greeley is a young and honest journalist who starts a newspaper called "Daily Star". Lucky Luke helps him to settle down at Dead End City, where he finds out how not everybody likes the truth.
name: Le Daily Star

description: A group of women arrive to a town where there is only men, to marry them. Jenny finds herself alone after her fiance is put in jail. Lucky Luke s appointed his substitute, temporarily. The Dalton learn all of this and kidnap Jenny.
name: La fiancee de Lucky Luke

description:
1- La ballade des Dalton¬†
2- Un amour de Jolly Jumper¬†
3- Grabuge a Pancake Valley¬†
4- L'ecole des sherifs
name: La ballade des Dalton et autres histoires

2- La bonne aventure¬†
3- La statue¬†
4- La flume¬†
name: Le ranch maudit

description: Union Pacific and Cenral Pacific are both building a railtrack from Sacramento to Omaha. To continue through the mountains, Central Pacific needs to bring Nitroglycerine, and Lucky Luke has to make sure it arrives, despite the Union Pacific trying everything they can to stop him.
name: Nitroglycerine

1- L'alibi¬†
2- Athletic city¬†
3- Ole Daltonitos¬†
4- Un cheval disparait
name: L'Alibi

description: The government offers a reward to the first person who makes the distance Missouri-California in less than ten days. Russell creates the Pony Express and Lucky Luke has to form the riders.
name: Le Pony Express

description:
Natasha and Walter are crew members on a charter flight for a soccer team destined for South America. The flight is also carrying a secret cargo of two crates of gold. A team of thugs will impersonate the soccer players and make it look like the plane crashed to divert the plane and take possession of the cargo.

After a missed landing in the Amazon rainforest, Natasha is separated from the rest of the group and falls into the hands of Indian guyapos, the dreaded head-hunters.

Walter will escape and join Natasha who managed to coax the tribe of the guyapos to join her. They use the natives to thwart the plans of the bandits, free the rest of the crew, and recover the gold.
name: Natacha, hotesse de l'air

description:
Mahmoud Zarrad, supreme leader of Kajastan attends parachute jumping exercises at a local airfield. Natacha who is a member of the flying club is aware of the head of state's intention to recruit Fairweather, a skydiving instructor, to train his paratroopers to invade an impregnable citadel where his rival, Prince Tchandra Abkar has taken refuge.

Furious at being rejected by the members of the club, Mahmoud Zarrad goes home. By chance he takes a flight to New Delhi, which Walter and Natacha are crew members. The aircraft is diverted to Kajastan to allow a child to be hospitalized for an emergency.

The Mararadjah takes the opportunity to keep Natacha in his country on charges of espionage in order to force her to convince Fairweather to train his paratroopers.

Thanks to the natives, Walter and Natacha avoid being executed and flee into the desert. Pursued by the traitor prince, they will be rescued by the rebels and lead to the refuge of Prince Tchandra ...
name: Natacha et le Maharadjah

description: After refusing to sell a house with a violent history to an eerie old man, Richard Ashwalt's life is coming apart at the seams under mysterious circumstances. Now separated from his family and falsely accused of murder, Richard is at his wits' end. Aided by policeman Al Sperry, Richard seeks Jebediah Crone, the man who began the course of events that have left Richard's life in shambles and driven him to the brink of insanity. As Richard investigates Crone and the mysteries that surround him, the pieces of a horrifying puzzle begin to fall into place-- but does he truly want to solve it?
name: 5 (of 6)

description: Kim the witch, feeling a premonition of a terrible threat that hangs over Dylan Dog , sends the magic cat Cagliostro to protect him. Meanwhile , Xabaras is finally getting the perfect version of his serum to restore life to the dead .
name: Xabaras!

description: Second half of the two issues story for the 20th anniversary of the title. While we discover some details of Dylan and Xabaras past, which partially contradict what we knew from issue #100, Dylan will have to finally make a choice about his father...
name: In nome del padre

description: The origin of Fell's Four is so huge, it's grown to two issues! While stranded in the Feywild, Adric recounts for Tisha how Fell's Four was born-and almost died the very same day. Join us as John Rogers brings us a new chapter in these thrilling adventures of swords and sorcery.
name: First Encounters, Part Two

description:
FEAR ITSELF TIE-IN

Loki needs allies to hatch his schemes. But what happens when the Trickster God cannot find a single one in Asgard? Follow Loki to the very depths of Hel as he wades through the dead to find someone to join his cause. But Loki will soon see that the dead do not forgive easily‚Ä¶or forget!
name: Feeling Hela Good

description: Mallory's secret history comes to a close with the grimmest revelations of all, leaving Hughie with a confession of his own to make. Everything is out in the open at last, in the final part of Barbary Coast.
name: Barbary Coast, Part Four

description: Cagliostro the Cat is back , and with him the shadow of the witches . A Lady is murdered in her bed , a man is tormented by premonitory dreams , a legend of an ancient damned tree ... A whirlwind of characters and mysteries caught in a vortex that falls ... into the cat's eye .
name: L'occhio del gatto

description: The first steps of Dylan as a nightmare investigator. From alcoholism to¬† resignation from Scotland Yard , from when he bought his galleon in a bottle to the first meeting with Groucho.
name: Il numero duecento

description: Are you shy ? You have no determination and everyone will tread on you ? The "disempathy" course by Professor Emerick promises to release your aggression . Even Ally , Dylan's girlfriend of the month , has followed the course , and she's now suspected of having killed an odious colleague . To learn more , Dylan takes the course and his character begins to change for worse ...
name: La legge della giungla

description: The class of Professor Emerick is¬† always crowded . Noone would say that his method of teaching disempathy , unleashing the latent wildness in all of us , would be inefficient. Even a convinced pacifist like Dylan , thanks to the advice of the illustrious teacher , can turn into a killing machine , indifferent and insensitive to the suffering of others . Fortunately, the investigator manages to escape the influence of Emerick and Mazu , the evil idol who inspired him ... And his choice , like all courageous choices , won't be meaningless.
name: Homo homini lupus

description: Pink Rabbit , the cartoon- rabbit , escapes once more from his world to get into ours. Meanwhile, Betty Bloom is at Dylan's office to find her ex-husband, one of the designers of the cartoon .
name: Il paese delle ombre colorate

description: When a man in a small town turns up dead, all evidence points to Jonah Hex as the shooter! On trial for his life in the backroom of a saloon, Hex must play detective if he's to prove his innocence. Artist Rafa Garres returns to illustrate this stand-alone potboiler!
name: Murder in Cottonwood

description:
IDW‚Äôs final farewell to the Angelverse is full of the creators who have been telling stories about the vampire with a soul from the very beginning. Each tale will be a farewell from the writers and artists who have known him best. Featuring the final new stories from the Angelverse!
¬†
  • ... Dust to Dust
  • OMG Unicorns
  • All The Time In The World
  • My Only Friend
  • Fight For The Remote
  • This One Time
  • A Blessing And "The Curse"
name: Yearbook

team_credits.name: Wolfram and Hart, Attorneys at Law

description: As they try to escape from prison, the Daltons find themselves in the cell of Synapse Burns, who is about to be released because he is amnesiac. The Daltons then pretend they have amnesia too.
name: L'amnesie des Dalton

description: Lucky Luke and Calamity Jane will try to solve the mystery of a town where stage coaches are attacked by a ghost.
name: Chasse aux fantomes

description: Ma Dalton tells her sons that the sheriff who put them in prison, Samuel Parker, is going to get married. The Daltons decide to escape and go to the wedding to kill him.
name: Les Dalon a la noce

description: Lucky Luke has to keep an eye on the construction of a bridge upon the Mississipi river, between St-Louis and Illinois Town. Bat Cayman, the mayor of both towns, this bridge means the end of his corrupted affairs, so he would do everything he can to stop the works.
name: Le pont sur le Mississippi

description: Belle Starr is a generous parishioner from Fort Smith who pays the bail of all the town's bandits. She creates a gang, in wich Lucky Luke wil try to infiltrate.
name: Belle Starr

description: There is a god rush at Klondike. Jasper, the butler of Waldo Badminton, is missing. Badminton and Lucky Luke start to look for him.
name: Le Klondike

description: There are elctions at Tombstone, and the candidates are Wyatt Earp and Old Clanton.
name: O.K. Corral

description: Marcel Dalton is the Daltons' oncle, an honest banker who arrives from Switzerland to run a small bank at Mosquito Gulch. Lucky Luke will escort him, as James Swindler, owner of a banking monopoly, hires the Daltons to chase their oncle.
name: Marcel Dalton

description: At the penitentiary, the Daltons make friends with Dunkle, a malicious and hallucinating prophet. They will escape together and go to Paradise Gulch, a town without sheriff, saloon, bank, money or armoury.
name: Le prophete

description: Frederick Remington is a painter who wants to make a portrait of indian chief Hiawatha. Lucky Luke will go with him.
name: L'artiste peintre

description: Buffalo Bill hires four comedians to impersonate the Daltons on his show, changing their personalities. The true Daltons escape later.
name: La legende de l'Ouest

description: Follows from the previous issue: This issues features the second and last part of the story about the birth of Shadow Brotherhood
name: Exodus

What has kept the planet intact ? And what is the role of the JNC - 9000 super - computer ? The explanation of these mysteries is on the Altrove base. Nathan and Martin join forces together with " Wild Goose " team composed by espers Michelle , Nicole and Vivian .
